Package com.foreach.across.modules.entity.util

Class EntityTypeDescriptor

java.lang.Object
com.foreach.across.modules.entity.util.EntityTypeDescriptor
public final class EntityTypeDescriptor extends Object
Represents the result of resolving a TypeDescriptor (for example from a property) to its best matching entity type. Mainly for internal use.
Since:
2.2.0
Author:
Arne Vandamme
